      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In RAM We have multiple obejcts created in the RAM \nin millions and RAM is Limited hence to save the RAM \nwe use the fly weight ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
