      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    Standard defination :- Flyweght uses sharing to support large number of fine gained objects efficiently",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    Standard defination :- Flyweght uses sharing to support large number of fine gained objects efficiently",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "XlmO0T8E94rcSpcOqvEWW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 419.738515067855,
      "y": 2103.3319477573787,
      "width": 438.21966552734375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ah",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1348038938,
      "version": 331,
      "versionNonce": 2021574195,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781464323242,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Intrinsic Stack :- Shared among object\nExtrinsic Stack :- Suplied by client externally",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Intrinsic Stack :- Shared among object\nExtrinsic Stack :- Suplied by client externally",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1lzDhqVCxnhBPy6nlauM6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 378.18942941834246,
      "y": 2178.0879788550455,
      "width": 1079.1192626953125,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ai",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 799443994,
      "version": 789,
      "versionNonce": 1942849491,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781464323242,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Use case :- Games like GTA 5, etc, Games \nText editor me multiple millions of char hota and we can colour a single chat or edit a singlefont \nnow if we keep the all chars object then it will blast the memory so we do is the, we keep \na to z alphabate flywright, so to render them we can use flyweight while for specific char we need it extrinsic\n\nTo save Memory in RAM, we need millions of object to be created but we can optimize it using flyweightsimple ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Use case :- Games like GTA 5, etc, Games \nText editor me multiple millions of char hota and we can colour a single chat or edit a singlefont \nnow if we keep the all chars object then it will blast the memory so we do is the, we keep \na to z alphabate flywright, so to render them we can use flyweight while for specific char we need it extrinsic\n\nTo save Memory in RAM, we need millions of object to be created but we can optimize it using flyweightsimple ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
